<div id="textRight">

	<h1>
			KFS | Solution-based Engineering Excellence		</h1>











<p>World-leaders in rotary kiln process and combustion optimisation, KFS was founded in 1999 by some of the industry&rsquo;s finest and most forward-thinking engineers and experts.</p>
<p>Our distinctiveness is based on the mastery of Computational Fluid Dynamics for burner design and system analysis backed up by an extensive history of physical modelling.</p>
<p>We now leverage and deploy our unique competencies in modelling, simulation and interpretation and associated process engineering to provide an outstanding range of products and services to customers operating in Process and Energy industries.</p>
<p>Equipment end users/operators, manufacturers or engineering integrators, we solve our customers&rsquo; flow, thermal, combustion and chemistry problems...</p>

	<a class="majorbutton" href="/offerings" onClick="ga('send', 'event', { eventCategory: 'cta', eventAction: 'click', eventLabel: 'solution-engineering', eventValue: 1});">Find Out More</a></div>



